    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "PAN\nAMERICAN AIRWAYS, INC.\nGENERAL OFFICES - CHRYSLER BUILDING\nNEW YORK CITY\nDecember\n1 9\n33\nMrs. H. M. Bixby,\nBolton Landing,\nNew York.\nMy dear Mrs. Bixby:\nI am sorry to have to tell you that your\nhusband informs us in a cable this morning that due to\nrecent developments in connection with our business in China,\nhe has had to put off his return home.\nI know you will\nbe deeply disappointed not to have him with you in time for\nChristmas,\nbut I hope that this will be merely a brief\npostponement and that he will be able to return before long.\nWith kindest regards.\nSincerely yours,\nSiMogan\nS. W. Morgan\nSWM: FP\ncc: Mr. Bixby\nCONTRACTORS TO THE UNITED STATES AND FOREIGN GOVERNMENTS FOR AIR MAIL SERVICE BETWEEN THE UNITED STATES AND THY\nWEST INDIES, MEXICO, CENTRAL AND SOUTE AMERICA"
    ],
